  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"animation\">animation</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label experimental\">experimental</label>\n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/animations\">@angular/animations</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a> } from <a href=\"api/animations\">'@angular/animations'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L844-L884\">animations/src/animation_metadata.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\nfunction <a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>(steps: <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a> | <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a>[], options: <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationOptions</a> | null = null): <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationReferenceMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationReferenceMetadata</a>;\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6yiij264hzhew66hp7un8fed7\"><code><a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a></code> 是一个特定于动画的函数，旨在用于 Angular 的动画 DSL 语言中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"da5qgyj96m3j3bfqaz7weqb4p\"><code>var myAnimation = <a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>(...)</code> 旨在生成一个可复用的动画，该动画可以在另一个动画或序列中被调用。可复用的动画旨在利用动画参数，并且生成的动画可以通过 \n<code><a href=\"api/animations/useAnimation\" class=\"code-anchor\">useAnimation</a></code> 方法使用。</p>\n<code-example>\nvar fadeAnimation = <a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>([\n  <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: '{{ start }}' }),\n  <a href=\"api/animations/animate\" class=\"code-anchor\">animate</a>('{{ time }}',\n    <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: '{{ end }}'}))\n], { params: { time: '1000ms', start: 0, end: 1 }});\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"65g5wt8j6tsl24eacvtdl0dzs\">如果将参数附加到动画，则它们充当\n<strong>默认参数值</strong>。当通过 \n<code><a href=\"api/animations/useAnimation\" class=\"code-anchor\">useAnimation</a></code> 调用动画时，允许直接传入参数值。如果传入的参数值中缺少任何值，则将使用默认值。</p>\n<code-example>\n<a href=\"api/animations/useAnimation\" class=\"code-anchor\">useAnimation</a>(fadeAnimation, {\n  params: {\n    time: '2s',\n    start: 1,\n    end: 0\n  }\n})\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6cficn8fen065pq1x5jq6clbg\">如果在动画之前缺少一个或多个参数值，则会抛出错误。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationAnimateRefMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationBuilder\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions\n - api/animations/AnimationQueryMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationReferenceMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationStaggerMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationTransitionMetadata\n - api/animations/query\n - api/animations/stagger\n - api/animations/transition\n - api/animations/trigger\n - api/animations/useAnimation\n - api/core/AnimationTransitionMetadata\n - api/core/Component\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions\n - api/animations/AnimationReferenceMetadata\n - api/animations/animate\n - api/animations/animation#animation\n - api/animations/animation#description\n - api/animations/style\n - api/animations/useAnimation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L844-L884\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/animations\n-->"
